==用車==
奧拉涅斯塔德電車使用2輛單層電車及2輛雙層電車行走，由[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[查茲沃斯_(加利福尼亞州)|查茲沃斯]]的{{lang|en|TIG/m}}公司製造<ref name="LATimes-May2015">{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-made-in-california-trolleymaker-20150527-story.html|title=Chatsworth trolley maker is going places|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-05-27|last=White|first=Ronald D.|access-date=2016-05-28|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016001550/https://www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-made-in-california-trolleymaker-20150527-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電車以[[氫|氫]]電池運行<ref name=tramz/>。

